      "writtenOn": "2021-06-03T14:02:26Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "seems fine, but what\u0027s this for? I get that there won\u0027t be a SDC in NGA, but concretely what is this unblocking us from doing? e.g. are we running these unit tests on a different device type already?\n",
